life.qbic.projectwizard.registration

Class OpenbisCreationController

  • java.lang.Object
    • life.qbic.projectwizard.registration.OpenbisCreationController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOpenbisCreationController

    public class OpenbisCreationController
extends Object
implements IOpenbisCreationController
    Provides methods to register new entities to openBIS using the openBIS Client API. Also performs some simple sanity checks before sending data to openBIS.
    Author:
    Andreas Friedrich
